<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>哈希 - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/%E5%93%88%E5%B8%8C/</link><description>哈希 - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/%E5%93%88%E5%B8%8C/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>密码学基础</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BD%AF%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E5%B1%82/%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/%E5%AF%86%E7%A0%81%E5%AD%A6%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BD%AF%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD%E5%B1%82/%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/%E5%AF%86%E7%A0%81%E5%AD%A6%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="密码学基础">密码学基础</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：密码学的三大基础工具是对称加密（快、共享密钥）、非对称加密（慢、公私钥分离）和哈希（不可逆、防篡改），实际系统中通常组合使用以兼顾安全与效率。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="密码学通过数学难题保障信息的机密性完整性和不可抵赖性">密码学通过数学难题保障信息的机密性、完整性和不可抵赖性</h2>
<h3 id="三大基础工具对比">三大基础工具对比</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>类型</th>
          <th>特点</th>
          <th>密钥</th>
          <th>用途</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>对称加密</td>
          <td>加解密速度快</td>
          <td>共享同一密钥</td>
          <td>大量数据加密</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>非对称加密</td>
          <td>加解密速度慢</td>
          <td>公钥/私钥配对</td>
          <td>密钥交换、数字签名</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>哈希</td>
          <td>单向不可逆</td>
          <td>无密钥</td>
          <td>数据完整性校验、密码存储</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="对称加密">对称加密</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">明文 + 密钥 → [加密算法] → 密文
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">密文 + 密钥 → [解密算法] → 明文
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">常见算法：AES、DES、3DES、SM4</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>算法</th>
          <th>密钥长度</th>
          <th>安全性</th>
          <th>说明</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>AES</td>
          <td>128/192/256位</td>
          <td>高</td>
          <td>目前主流标准</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>DES</td>
          <td>56位</td>
          <td>低</td>
          <td>已被暴力破解</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>3DES</td>
          <td>168位</td>
          <td>中</td>
          <td>DES的加强版，已逐步淘汰</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>SM4</td>
          <td>128位</td>
          <td>高</td>
          <td>国密标准</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="非对称加密">非对称加密</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">加密：明文 + 公钥 → 密文    解密：密文 + 私钥 → 明文
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">签名：明文 + 私钥 → 签名    验签：签名 + 公钥 → 验证
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">常见算法：RSA、ECC、SM2</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>算法</th>
          <th>密钥长度</th>
          <th>特点</th>
          <th>适用场景</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>RSA</td>
          <td>2048/4096位</td>
          <td>成熟广泛</td>
          <td>数字签名、HTTPS握手</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>ECC</td>
          <td>256位</td>
          <td>同等安全下密钥更短</td>
          <td>移动端、IoT资源受限场景</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>SM2</td>
          <td>256位</td>
          <td>国密标准</td>
          <td>国内合规要求</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="哈希函数">哈希函数</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">任意长度输入 → [哈希算法] → 固定长度输出（不可逆）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">特性：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 相同输入 → 相同输出
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 不同输入 → 输出几乎一定不同（碰撞概率极低）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 无法从输出反推输入</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>算法</th>
          <th>输出长度</th>
          <th>安全性</th>
          <th>说明</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>SHA-256</td>
          <td>256位</td>
          <td>高</td>
          <td>目前主流</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>SHA-3</td>
          <td>可变</td>
          <td>高</td>
          <td>新一代标准</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>MD5</td>
          <td>128位</td>
          <td>低</td>
          <td>已发现碰撞，不推荐</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>SM3</td>
          <td>256位</td>
          <td>高</td>
          <td>国密标准</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<hr>
<h2 id="常见问题与误区">常见问题与误区</h2>
<h3 id="问题1明文传输密钥">问题1：明文传输密钥</h3>
<p><strong>根因</strong>：对称加密的密钥在传输过程中被截获
<strong>解决</strong>：使用非对称加密交换对称密钥（如TLS握手），或采用安全的密钥分发机制</p>]]></description></item></channel></rss>